&lt;p&gt;Charles H. Schulz (França)&lt;br&gt; Mobile: +33 6 98655424 – E-mail: &lt;a href="mailto:charles.schulz@documentfoundation.org"&gt;charles.schulz@documentfoundation.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Italo Vignoli (Itália)&lt;br&gt; Mobile: +39 348 5653829 – E-mail: &lt;a href="mailto:italo.vignoli@documentfoundation.org"&gt;italo.vignoli@documentfoundation.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
